<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3672] MapReduce test cases shouldn&apos;t use system /tmp</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3672</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Right now some of our MR test cases seem to put local directories in /tmp - this can cause conflicts when running multiple builds on the same Hudson box. We should instead use a build/tmp directory for this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
